= CodeSelect with pipes =
Use

<pre>
{{!}}
</pre>

rather than

<pre>
|
</pre>

Or simply have a look at the mediawiki markup for the following example.

<!-- EDITORS NOTE: '{{!}}' is a magic word for '|'.-->
{{CodeSelect|code=
Exec=cat file {{!}} grep something
}}

